In addition, we assist businesses in getting the right advisory support from our unique network of professional.

Our team comprises industry experts within the legal, finance, technology and marketing sectors. We have led companies, advised major brands and contributed to the growth and success of numerous small to medium and large businesses around the world.

THE

COMPANY

We add value to our clients through two key methods, Consultancy Services and our Exclusive Global Network.
CONSULTANCY SERVICES

We accelerate international expansion, acting as your business partner to increase and generate new revenue. Our market entry services range from creating a local strategy for your target market to establishing operations through partnerships, setting up a local subsidiary or investing in an existing international company to grow your business. We provide customized solutions at every stage of your international journey through our technology-enabled approach to developing long-term success in your own business.

EXCLUSIVE GLOBAL NETWORK

Our unique experience over the past 20 years, has allowed us to develop a powerful network, and nurture strong relationships with local governments, global institutions and businesses. We want to use our experience and international reach to make a significant difference to your pipeline and revenue streams. Our international network will join forces with you to take you on a collective journey of growth. We will delve into your needs as a business and guide you every step of the way to make the most meaningful and effective connections. In addition to peer networking and introductions via our online portal, we host regular events, including workshops, lunches and away days, as well as run various initiatives to add the maximum value to our members.

THE

JOURNEY

We have over 20 years' experience working in legal services and management consultancy, with our leadership team having previously set up their own professional servicesâ firm and scaling it to 50 offices internationally.
FOUNDERS
1990s
Assisted UK businesses in entering new emerging markets and vice versa
DOT COM
2000s
Utilised technological advancements to really help businesses grow.
SCALE UP
2010s
Exponential growth made the founders realize the need for Centuro Global
INCEPTION
2018
We very quickly learnt that the key to success is a balanced combination of what you know and who you know. The foundations of any business is a high quality product or service. However, building key professional relationships can take you to the next level and elevate your business to the top. Some might even say that your network is your net worth. We therefore decided to create Centuro Global, an exclusive business hub.
TODAY
2019
Over the years we have all spent countless hours attending general networking events, trying to connect to people through family and friends, through LinkedIn and other tools. However, such methods are not a focused approach and not the most efficient use of time. We quickly realised that having a dedicated network of high quality individuals to tap into, all in one place, would be the best way for entrepreneurs to take their businesses to the next level.
In order to grow your business quickly you need to be able to help others to succeed. Everyone should give and everyone will receive. We have therefore created the Centuro Business Hub to connect high calibre Entrepreneurs, SMEs, Professional Services providers and Investors. This has been our journey and now we want to help you with your journey.

THE

MISSION

We want to help all businesses grow to their best ability and connect them with the right people to take them to the next level.

CORE

TEAM

ASMA BASHIR
CHAIRMAN
Asma has worked in the legal services industry for most of her career, having been with multinational law firms before she established her own practice. Asma went on to found Newland Chase, where she worked for 13 years before the firm was eventually acquired by an American corporation. Asma continued within that business to help grow the global brand having established hubs across four continents and expanding the services to global jurisdictions. Since departing that business Asma is now working with entrepreneurs and investors to help their journey through growth and expansion to international markets. She is a mentor on the Mayor's International Business Programme as well as a Senator for the World Business Angel Forum. Asma has worked with both multinational clients and SME's to help them expand into complex regions across the world. Her specialist skills are to match entrepreneurs and scaling companies to the right investor either for funding, merger or acquisition.
ZAIN ALI
CHIEF EXECUTIVE OFFICER
Zain started his career as an Intellectual Property lawyer advising large multinational media, sports, and technology companies on how to protect their brands and creative content. He branched out to advising start ups and scale ups, exposing him to some key challenges that all entrepreneurs face and inspiring him to start Centuro Global with Asma. He has also travelled extensively and spent time living and working in Argentina and Beijing. What distinguishes Zain from other lawyers is his sharp analytical skills and commercial awareness to truly help businesses grow internationally. Zain has a first class degree in History and is a qualified solicitor.
ZAFAR MIRZA
CHIEF OPERATING OFFICER
Zafar has been an entrepreneur for more than 20 years, having started his first business at an early age. His specialist skills are within international expansion and supporting companies with government liaison around the world. He has significant experience in the Middle East and Asia having assisted clients with complex problems in these regions. Zafar is a new market entry specialist providing valuable insights into expanding overseas with a focus on risk and compliance. Zafar previously worked on global projects for large multinational companies and is now supporting entrepreneurs succeed at an international level.
ZACK TOPUZOV
ADVISOR
Zack began his career at a public accounting firm based in Chicago, USA. His core focus was on audit and consulting engagements for startups and financial institutions. Following 4 years of working in the US, he moved to London where he continues to work in a similar capacity. As a dual qualified US/UK accountant, Zack brings great value to the Centuro Global advisory team. Zack's skills and experience are highly valued by entrepreneurs as he has a unique insight into analysing clients' financial models and providing accurate and realistic projections to be successful.
BEN CALEGARI
ADVISOR
Ben is a software engineer from New Hampshire. Having worked both in Silicon Valley and Massachusetts, Ben has extensive experience building and deploying software for startups and multinational companies. His technical knowledge and startup experience is an invaluable addition to the Centuro Global advisory team.
